<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1938392-what-do-people-think-happened-to-nimue">What do people think happened to Nimue?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1938392'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F68521.Excalibur">like</a></span>

