<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1751548-how-does-derfel-wind-up-in-a-monastery">How does Derfel wind up in a monastery? The last I recallwas that he was on the shore watching Arthur float off into the mist. What did I miss?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1751548'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F68521.Excalibur">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1751548-how-does-derfel-wind-up-in-a-monastery">one year ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1751548-how-does-derfel-wind-up-in-a-monastery">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/75254779-rose-gan"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/75254779-rose-gan">Rose Gan</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    He had pledged himself to bishop Sansum when he was forced to become a Christian in return for Morgan lifting the curse from Ceinwyn.. When Meurig's t<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    He had pledged himself to bishop Sansum when he was forced to become a Christian in return for Morgan lifting the curse from Ceinwyn.. When Meurig's troops arrives to the battle of Camlann, Sansum is with them. He commands Derfel to come to him. Derfel answers My Lord... although he actually means Arthur, who is sailing away. From then on Derfel is now in the service of Sansum. At some point in the future, Sansum founded the monastery and after the death of Ceinwyn, Derfel must have become a monk at the direction of Sansum. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
 <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

